headline.print_headline: Peruvian Developer Ready to Remake Old Car Plant
headline.main: Peruvian Developer Ready to Remake Old Car Plant

lead_paragraph: Peruvian developer Fernando Palazuelo says he is ready to begin clearing rubble and trash from part of Detroit's massive Packard car plant.
